when a link is clicked on in the nav bar a line will appear underneath, the width of the text

when a project div is rolled over it will receive a darkened transparency effect
or 
when a project div is rolled over the box changes to solid colour and displays logo and project info


when work is clicked on the nav bar a sub menu will slide down
the option clicked on the sub menu will change to another colour

The second layer of project options will display with the same effect as the first (description above)

when clicked through to the inner pages, only the middle content displaying the work will scroll down. the two side panels remain static.